{
  "id": "RAW_44bddc97",
  "title": "面壁智能发布 EdgeClaw 智能体框架，主打安全和省钱",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1NDA4NjU2MA==&mid=2247659346&idx=2&sn=dff63653a2743e233ab33a6d1edb13b3",
  "date": "2026-03-21 05:31:00",
  "author": "AI前线",
  "siteName": "AI前线",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <p style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #919191;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;margin: 0;margin-top: 13px;padding-left: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者 | OpenBMB</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">当前大火的 OpenClaw，让越来越多开发者和个人用户意识到个人智能体发挥的巨大作用。然而在实际使用过程中，有两个问题被使用者广泛提及：一是用户个人数据会被 OpenClaw 上传给云端大模型，造成一定程度的个人数据泄露；另一方面是 OpenClaw 执行过程中拼接的超长上下文带来 token 浪费，造成了较高的使用成本。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">3月19日，我们正式发布并开源由 THUNLP，中国人民大学，AI9Stars，面壁智能 与 OpenBMB 基于 OpenClaw 联合开发的安全高效端云协同智能体框架 EdgeClaw，通过<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">三级安全协同</span>与<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">性价比感知协同机制</span>，解决 OpenClaw 使用过程中本地数据泄漏、token 花费成本高等问题。通过部署在 DGXSpark、MacMini 等桌面端设备上，给使用者带来安全高效的本地龙虾使用体验。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-style: italic;\">➤ &nbsp;GitHub 链接🔗&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/Openbmb/EdgeClaw\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/Openbmb/EdgeClaw</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:20px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 500;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;height: 59px;line-height: 85px;color: #4285f4;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;border-bottom: 2px solid #4285f4;background-size: 57px auto;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=841fe63b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm55iaBw4iatPevGfMCdiaIHVIXdxtONt9two1Ie4VSMLzPwvJnogdaPabx4wzYwzYdVykwe3ib5m5un9NP3LeuHmrYdRBsHwxzCkjA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">EdgeClaw：安全高效端云协同智能体</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">当下 AI Agent 架构中，端侧长期被忽视——所有数据与任务一股脑涌向云端，隐私泄露与算力浪费由此而生。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">EdgeClaw 通过<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;三级安全协同机制</span>&nbsp;实现本地数据加密与安全隔离，通过&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">性价比感知协同机制</span>&nbsp;灵活调用不同费用模型，实现简单任务使用低价模型、复杂任务调用高阶模型。安全协同和性价比感知协同运行在&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">同一管线</span>&nbsp;中，通过权重和两阶段短路策略协同工作。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">EdgeClaw 主体功能实现以 OpenClaw 插件形式加载，配合端云协同的智能转发能力，开发者无需修改业务逻辑，即可在 EdgeClaw 中实现“公开数据上云、敏感数据脱敏、私密数据落地”的无感端云协同隐私保护与性价比节省。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:20px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 500;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;height: 59px;line-height: 85px;color: #4285f4;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;border-bottom: 2px solid #4285f4;background-size: 57px auto;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=90d5a05e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm4uuamsgu6rMdhElO07FuD7Wc8wh4bJDUvD6GxiaJ8ovH6Zgok4RTlibjicmdWkMzNfxviaekosWeI44nBwZC0KmoyZ0tVZ9oiaR1As%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">三级安全协同机制</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">EdgeClaw 的一个核心创新是自研三级安全协同机制：通过在 OpenClaw 执行流程中植入 Hook，EdgeClaw 能自动将每一条用户消息、工具调用参数和 Agent 输出按敏感程度分为三级：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">S1：默认模式（信息将在云端处理），可直接用云端模型处理。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">S2 脱敏模式（信息将在脱敏后处理），自动脱敏，将企业的敏感信息模糊化（如把「王小二」变成「员工 A」）后，再发往云端。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">S3：安全模式（信息将强制在本地处理），物理隔离，敏感数据完全留在本地，由预装的 MiniCPM 系列模型离线处理。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">对于隐私文件，EdgeClaw 识别为 S3 等级并由本地模型离线处理</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在三级分类基础上，EdgeClaw 使用了基于规则检测器和本地 LLM 检测器的双检测引擎，两个引擎可组合叠加，通过 checkpoints 配置按场景灵活启用。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.16666666666666666\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=67c14ccd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F30ME92wwXJmKq5eSicunfh7WlnQD9JlXuYhBWbGZNjzNUQibKF9YGIEib4iauMOyq9XPtXiaRAPo60JcsZh6Y1F3NO5Fw3mD4P6AZ6kDsuq2T7uw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D2\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">与此同时，EdgeClaw 还维护了一套「双轨记忆」机制——云端模型只能看到脱敏后的对话历史，只有本地模型才能访问包含完整信息的记忆内容，从根本上杜绝了隐私数据通过上下文窗口泄露给第三方云服务的风险。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:20px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 500;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;height: 59px;line-height: 85px;color: #4285f4;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;border-bottom: 2px solid #4285f4;background-size: 57px auto;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=13fbdca5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm4zeNRE1Fdic1KapHXJN68evrz9JrDLLumVjDfib7G5IjwEy8kuib1BNt4TxCo5Jn99hONx2OlFbAPovibqREuRorCVahfIrrRoCfc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">性价比感知协同机制</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在典型的 AI 编程助手工作流中，大部分请求是查文件、看代码、简单问答——用最贵的模型处理这些任务会造成大量浪费。性价比感知协同用本地小模型做 LLM-as-Judge，把请求按复杂度分级路由到不同价位的云端模型。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.29907407407407405\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b3de91e7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F30ME92wwXJlxNT4VLiaenWXHP3ia5ACgnSHbrzjSzNafBfRvM7p2JEecLS24dv0OtCHibNZzkSx0P8wUQwXauiaiagXAFN2iarhub3gToL8kfu1EE%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D4\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">表 路由模型配置示例</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">实际测试中，以典型编程助手工作流为例，性价比感知协同机制可将 60–80% 的请求路由到更便宜的模型。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:20px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 500;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;height: 59px;line-height: 85px;color: #4285f4;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;border-bottom: 2px solid #4285f4;background-size: 57px auto;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=831ea6a8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm612GnXuXIkLb1icqZRjoCoVS6Tvhj4HgNwoiboYRbcTfgOfhqCJAib2OfOmfIsp4ompHibCXlsFqumvElBXCrOZXyTeOibiag0v5ibqk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">可组合路由管线</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">安全协同和性价比感知协同运行在<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">同一管线</span>中，通过权重和两阶段短路策略协同工作。管线设计遵循安全优先：安全路由器高权重先跑，有敏感数据就直接短路处理，不浪费时间再判断复杂度。只有安全通过（S1）后，才启动性价比感知协同优化成本。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.5703703703703704\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7a671013&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2F30ME92wwXJnlFDwhploGHLvBB4E2icA6WJnKJJBK7EAUuZ6qlRpfv53aJoRyaw2MpM9qlYicPO56kTw0n5na8IIvXvz7Y3WVX1RG14Ejpdvh0%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D6\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:20px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 500;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;height: 59px;line-height: 85px;color: #4285f4;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;border-bottom: 2px solid #4285f4;background-size: 57px auto;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1d40de8f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm6YuzDVd2KwX9Vich4Yag2kUkjmxPcRahof5uMWyib4srlBZUVLuwfXbia4BN0OxC3iarnliaWf7COxMBIdl07NWhx6dobMj2icsvaao%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">未来规划</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">EdgeClaw 将持续迭代，进化为支持更广泛端侧设备部署的软件系统。未来的开发计划包含如下四个部分：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">EdgeClaw Router。聚焦安全高效端云协同，结合更多端侧硬件与模型，实现更灵活多样的本地模型选择。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">EdgeClaw Memory。优化 OpenClaw 记忆，实现面向任务的记忆机制，实现智能体真正配合用户执行长期复杂任务的能力。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">EdgeClaw SkillHub。构建聚焦支持本地化任务的 Skill Hub，整合端侧智能体服务关注的特定 Skill 并内置高频使用 Skill。对于主流的基于 AI 模型实现的 Skill 实现端侧模型替代，进一步提高使用效率。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">EdgeClaw UI。支持更加端侧场景友好的前端 UI 设计，增加本地 GPU 使用率、本地 token 使用量等端侧用户关注的性能监控指标。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">EdgeClaw 聚焦构建安全高效的端云协同智能体，未来将继续保持开源。欢迎广大开发者与行业伙伴一起参与贡献，共同打造“多、快、好、省”的端侧智能体解决方案。</span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "面壁智能联合多家机构发布 EdgeClaw 框架，通过三级安全协同与性价比路由机制，解决个人智能体在隐私泄露与 Token 成本方面的痛点。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "面壁智能联合多家机构发布 EdgeClaw 框架，通过三级安全协同与性价比路由机制，解决个人智能体在隐私泄露与 Token 成本方面的痛点。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了由面壁智能、OpenBMB、清华 THUNLP 等联合开发的 EdgeClaw 框架。该框架旨在解决 OpenClaw 等个人智能体在实际应用中面临的个人数据泄露和 Token 使用成本高昂两大难题。EdgeClaw 核心采用了“三级安全协同”与“性价比感知协同”机制，通过将任务按敏感度和复杂度进行分级路由，实现敏感数据本地化处理（利用 MiniCPM 模型）以及简单任务低价化处理。此外，框架还引入了“双轨记忆”机制，确保云端模型仅接触脱敏信息，从工程层面构建了“多、快、好、省”的端云协同智能体解决方案。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "自研三级安全协同机制实现隐私分级保护。",
      "explanation": "通过 Hook 植入，将数据分为默认、脱敏和安全三级。S3 级敏感数据强制由本地 MiniCPM 模型离线处理，实现物理隔离，确保私密数据不上传云端。"
    },
    {
      "point": "性价比感知协同机制大幅降低智能体运行成本。",
      "explanation": "利用本地小模型作为 Judge，根据任务复杂度将请求路由至不同价位的云端模型。实测在编程助手场景下，可将 60-80% 的请求分流至低成本模型。"
    },
    {
      "point": "安全优先的可组合路由管线确保合规性。",
      "explanation": "安全协同与性价比协同运行在同一管线中，安全路由器拥有更高权重。一旦识别到敏感数据，系统将直接触发短路策略，优先保障数据安全而非成本优化。"
    },
    {
      "point": "双轨记忆机制从根源杜绝上下文隐私泄露。",
      "explanation": "系统维护两套记忆，云端模型仅能获取脱敏后的对话历史，而包含完整信息的记忆仅存储于本地并由本地模型访问，防止隐私通过上下文窗口泄露给第三方。"
    }
  ],
